<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/3" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style=""></iframe></p>
<p><strong>聚餐</strong></p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scythr" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5099361); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5099361&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609720559" alt="Scythr" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5099361)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scythr" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5099361); return false;">Scythr</a></span></p>
<p><strong>人事页：</strong>以后&#8230;会有的</p>
<p>希望你有一个愉快的阅读体验，我，我尽量&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</td>
